title: Royal Holloway launches its Women Inspire campaign (Royal Holloway, University of London)
text: ( Source : Royal Holloway, University of London ) Royal Holloway, University of London is launching its Women Inspire Campaign this week to celebrate inspirational women and their achievements and continue the legacy of its Victorian founders.
